{"tid":1254694,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[進擊的巨人]梟揀格里沙既正真原因!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! (我估)","createTime":"2019-06-24T08:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T13:41:06.000Z","uid":156666,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd357e9071fa42cf1f25491d79663128e18dc9b","tid":1254694,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"首先我地知道梟靠巨人之力係可以睇到未來<br />\n而係最新一集佢話揀格里沙既原因係「佢走左出牆外」<br />\n但佢同時亦有講「如果佢冇走出牆」會點 而且係詳細講出佢地既人生會向咩方向走<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係唔係暗示 格里沙本人係特別既存在?<br />\n所有其他人做既野都用遵從梟記憶中所見到既野 所以佢先可以詳細講出佢地既人生會向咩方向走<br />\n但只有格里沙做出左同佢記憶中所見到既野唔同既行動<br />\n所以梟真正揀格里沙既原因係因為佢覺得格里沙本人有「改變命運走向既特別能力」所以先揀佢?"},{"pid":"5b00b7032660f8ed9f9fea861cbfc708d3077cb0","tid":1254694,"uid":198822,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n梟係話如果冇行出去 格里沙兩兄妹嘅生活&quot;好可能&quot;會點"},{"pid":"c03e8cbad27e40f417917d102c0e3579d7caaa1e","tid":1254694,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252903d2a2836e33ec17c747e04c814ae386c2e5","tid":1254694,"uid":52590,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:07:35.000Z","msg":"係因為佢有 追求自由既渴望"},{"pid":"8d74174633456dcbdf108d51c7013066d3151be7","tid":1254694,"uid":156666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T09:43:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc03463fec4d758d9edec7c4b86011f78246db22","tid":1254694,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dis